Ser '''Arryk Cargyll''' is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. He is long dead before the start of the series, and thus is not expected to appear. Arryk Cargyll was a renowned [[knight]], and member of the [[Kingsguard]] who fought and died in the [[Dance of the Dragons]].
